      • addDataPoint

        public void addDataPoint​(State current,
                         Action action,
                         State next,
                         double reward,
                         double qvalue)
        Constructs and adds a DataPoint to the collection of DataPoints being stored within the DataManager.
        Parameters:
        current - the current State.
        action - the Action executed in the current State.
        next - the resulting next State from executing the Action in the current State.
        reward - the produced reward for executing the Action in the current State.
        qvalue - the calculated Q-Value for the (State, Action, State, reward) tuple.
